{"tid":584074,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日小食] 蜜糖雜錦果仁小食","createTime":"2018-03-07T14:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T19:23:07.000Z","uid":43041,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f934ed249839ecf8c0b32bcad485e0dfac417b36","tid":584074,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:07:20.000Z","msg":"今次又係模仿遊戲Skyrim既野食<br />\n雖然外觀望落去唔太似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋今次份小食真係好撚肥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/214841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F214841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3bddfd20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雜錦果仁 麥片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/214849_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F214849_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=16a5612c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蜜糖，鹽，砂糖，水，牛油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/215658_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F215658_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=69b6c041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果仁鳩切<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/215749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F215749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=678b22f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切完同麥片攪勻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/215811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F215811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=59b958d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將濕既材料煮滾，中火煮10分鐘，期間不斷攪動。厚身後熄火。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/215911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F215911_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1eaaae2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等個糖漿無咁辣手就可以續d續d咁加入果仁麥片裏面。盡力攪勻，然後用手壓成球狀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/220112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F220112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=15ac03ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/220201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F220201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9ee82bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上碟<br />\n特登整唔同大細，好似跟翻game入面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食譜：<a href=\"https://tastesoftamriel.tumblr.com/post/159066717707/honey-nut-treat-this-dainty-treat-can-be-found\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftastesoftamriel.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F159066717707%2Fhoney-nut-treat-this-dainty-treat-can-be-found&d=dANmUINyULLXl1SVtOyhvwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0af9b51c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tastesoftamriel.tumblr.com/post/159066717707/honey-nut-treat-this-dainty-treat-can-be-found</a>"},{"pid":"bbaa13c960ed8fcb626a186b7fb6e9b58b5f3452","tid":584074,"uid":41781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"巴打你條頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050ba2f6e64de1a7d39b4424e1